Turkey's trade deficit widened to 382 mlndlrs in April from 275 mln in March and 273 mln in April 1986,the State Statistics Institute said.    The deficit for the first quarter of 1987 widened to 1.23billion dlrs from 1.20 billion a year earlier.    April exports totalled 702 mln dlrs compared with importsof 1.08 billion.    Exports in the first four months were worth 2.69 billiondlrs compared with imports of 3.92 billion. REUTER&#3;